metadata.name: Lucia
metadata.description:
This is a story of love and hate for photography, for beauty,
I always need to bring the subject into my world and push the model to give more emotions, 
I want to establish a relationship with the subject, a special relationship.
It is something I am capable of accomplishing,
I am looking for an impactful image, which arrives directly without compromise.
My research is always linked to stealing an inner beauty
I love portraits, in a disruptive way.
I am intrigued by imperfections.
